      <prov.body>
        <subprov skeleton="no">
          <label auto.number="no" denominator="no"/>
          <para>
            <text>The purpose of this Act is to ensure regional councils are able to take into account the effect of greenhouse gas emissions on climate change, including whenâ€”</text>
